summary: Okay, this marvel, avenge the fallen posters were bugging me so much. They align perfectly for a head movement. So i had to do...
caption:
Okay, this marvel, avenge the fallen posters were bugging me so much. They align perfectly for a head movement. So i had to do this.

There is 2 version of this  i can see but i only made this one. It starts with Peter looking down and ends with Tony looking up. Black and white ones are more sad and colored ones are more ready to fight.

I know i messed up in the middle and there is something wrong with the flow. Maybe it is because Rocket or Carol.

Did you ever notice Fury, Valkyrie, Clint and Gamora is the only noes looking directly into camera?

title: Running From My Shadow
body:
Loki has escaped the Asgard prison, again.

Soft Praise To a Hard Lie

It had become one of his favorite hobbies, if not the only one. Sneaking out of prison every other day was something that filled Loki with joy, whether it was to steal something or play pranks on Thor…
